15
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:51,630
[Goodbye My Princess]

16
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:56,670
[Episode 23]

17
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,730
You wretched servant!

18
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:21,780
What kind of feud do you have with the Xi State's Ninth Princess that you must harm her this way?

19
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:29,100
Your Majesty, there's a matter that I want to report.

20
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:30,510
Say it!

21
00:02:31,370 --> 00:02:37,150
The bowl of fungus pear soup that Ninth Princess took in originally belonged to Crown Prince.

22
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:40,800
Crown Prince saw that Ninth Princess liked to eat it,

23
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:44,980
so he gave his bowl to Ninth Princess.

24
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,050
Is that true?

25
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:56,790
Replying to Your Imperial Majesty. That is indeed what happened.

26
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:02,900
Oh my! So this wretched servant was intending to poison you, Your Highness the Crown Prince!

27
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,730
And I was wondering

28
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:15,300
why Prince Yi didn't consider his lofty position and jumped out to fight for you.

29
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:20,000
When he left, he didn't take you with him and instead left you behind to receive punishment in the Crown Prince Manor.

30
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:25,290
Talk. Was it Prince Yi who commanded you to poison the crown prince?!

31
00:03:27,570 --> 00:03:31,100
Li Yan, how dare you accuse Prince Yi in such a manner?!

32
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:34,830
I have a basis for it. The material evidence and eyewitness are all here!

33
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:38,560
Imperial Father, please do not listen to Li Yan's nonsense.

34
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:42,900
Fifth Brother would definitely not commit such a rebellious act of defying one's superior.

35
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,850
Your Imperial Majesty, spare my life!

36
00:03:48,850 --> 00:03:50,580
- Ceng Xian!
- Here!

37
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:56,040
Immediately bring your troop to Prince Yi Manor, seal it and search it! No one may enter or leave without my decree!

38
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,460
Yes!

39
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:03,120
- Immediately return to the palace. Send someone to notify Prime Minister Gao as soon as possible.
- Yes.

40
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:09,320
Who are you people?! How dare you trespass into here?!

41
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,710
Move aside!

42
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,110
What is happening?

43
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:21,550
Per His Imperial Majesty's decree, the Prince Yi Mansion is placed on lockdown.

44
00:04:21,550 --> 00:04:24,950
No one may leave without His Imperial Majesty's permission.

45
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:27,120
What?

46
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:56,530
[Court of Judicial Review]

47
00:04:57,460 --> 00:05:02,730
Talk. Who incited you to poison the crown prince?

48
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:20,650
Everything was my idea.

49
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:27,180
I hated the crown prince for punishing me.

50
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:30,730
No one else commanded me.

51
00:05:36,330 --> 00:05:39,540
Don't! Don't!

52
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:47,010
Once you enter the Court of Judicial Review, you won't be able to avoid the torture.

53
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:51,000
But it would be suspicious if you confessed immediately after the torture has just started.

54
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:55,200
Your testimony would then be unbelievable.

55
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:59,150
However, even the toughest bones can not hold out

56
00:05:59,150 --> 00:06:01,610
for more than three days inside the Court of Judicial Review.

57
00:06:01,610 --> 00:06:06,260
I understand. I must persist up to three days for them to believe my words.

58
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:09,200
I will wait until that day to make the confession.

59
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,040
I appreciate your suffering.

60
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,740
It is my honor to work for Your Highness.

61
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,220
I will never forget your kindness

62
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,830
that Your Highness has shown me.

63
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:37,110
I will take care of your family. Don't worry.

64
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,500
You are really a tough one.

65
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:56,090
However, we have plenty of methods here to get you to open your mouth.

66
00:06:56,620 --> 00:07:01,700
I advise you to clearly think about it soon to avoid bodily pains.

67
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,510
My Lady! Hurry!

68
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:24,400
Hurry up!

69
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:25,740
Stop!

70
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,710
Elder Brother!

71
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:28,950
Where are you going at this late hour?

72
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:31,600
I just...

73
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:35,450
Do you know that Prince Yi Manor is now surrounded by the Shenwu Army?

74
00:07:35,450 --> 00:07:38,320
Not only you, but even a fly can't fly into there!

75
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:41,270
But Brother, Prince Yi is in trouble right now!

76
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:44,500
Am I supposed to just sit in our manor, worry and do nothing?

77
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:47,530
If I can just see him, I would be a little bit less worried.

78
00:07:47,530 --> 00:07:51,690
What do girls know? If you make one wrong move,

79
00:07:51,690 --> 00:07:54,200
our Zhao family will lose the whole game, too.

80
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:57,620
Prince Yi is currently unable to protect himself. I will not allow you to get involved in these muddy waters, either!

81
00:07:57,620 --> 00:08:00,060
No! I must go out today!

82
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:02,600
Come back! Servants!

83
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,750
- Send Lady back into her room!
- Let me go!

84
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:06,820
- She is not allowed to leave without my orders!
- Let go of me!

85
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,130
- Brother!
- My Lady!

86
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:10,100
- Brother!
- My Lady!

87
00:08:10,100 --> 00:08:14,720
Let me go! Let go! Brother!

88
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:18,510
[Embracing the Moon Pavilion]

89
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:31,930
It's almost the third day. Where is the antidote?

90
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,520
Princess!

91
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:13,460
You want to change into palace clothing? I'll go get them for you.

92
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:48,340
Your Highness.

93
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:51,380
Isn't this the Danchi servant who is always by the ninth princess' side?

94
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:56,330
She is usually wearing a Danchi outfit. Why has she changed into clothes from the Li Empire today?

95
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,970
What are you doing?

96
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,610
You've worked hard.

97
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:34,700
Your Highness, in my opinion, we don't have to bother with this servant.

98
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:39,010
She is not only a mute, but also stupid.

99
00:10:40,730 --> 00:10:46,060
I know you're worried about the ninth princess, but the person who poisoned her is Prince Yi.

100
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:49,200
If you want the antidote, you shouldn't find me.

101
00:10:56,900 --> 00:11:00,910
Go back. Kneeling here won't do anything.

102
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,820
Let go!

103
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:37,170
Your Highness, it's been three days already.

104
00:12:37,170 --> 00:12:41,500
Tomorrow morning at the imperial court, the witnesses and evidence will be presented to His Imperial Majesty.

105
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:44,700
It's over for Li Chengyin.

106
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:52,920
- Search the place!
- Yes!

107
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:01,400
- This way!
- Yes!

108
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:03,800
- Look carefully!
- That way!

109
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:06,390
- We didn't find anything!
- Look over there!

110
00:14:06,390 --> 00:14:07,830
Look over there!

111
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:09,480
- Search!
- Okay!

112
00:14:15,850 --> 00:14:17,840
General, we found it!

113
00:14:20,290 --> 00:14:21,540
Let's go!

114
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:57,320
A'Du, why are you here?

115
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,920
Xiaofeng is in trouble?

116
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:20,640
A'Du.

117
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:55,730
She has been poisoned using a Western Border mysterious poison, Blood Thorns.

118
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:59,930
It's too late to make the remedy now.

119
00:15:59,930 --> 00:16:02,800
I know a way to force the poison out of her.

120
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:06,170
A'Du, go and fill two copper tubs with clean water.

121
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:08,330
Then, guard the door for three incenses time (1 1/2 hours to 3 hours).

122
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:11,210
No matter what happens, don't let anyone in.

