♫  The night hasn't ended, as the river of stars flowed alone  ♫

129
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:26,960
♫ The sky is clear, the scenery is good  ♫

130
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:31,200
♫ If you're not by my side, so what if I can go up the Firmament ♫

