374
00:40:47,950 --> 00:40:52,900
There are no outsiders here. Tell me your opinions.

375
00:40:58,680 --> 00:41:02,690
Fifth Brother and I are blood siblings.

376
00:41:02,690 --> 00:41:05,340
I don't believe that he would do something like this.

377
00:41:05,340 --> 00:41:09,840
But the Court of Judicial Review has already obtained testimony from a witness.

378
00:41:09,840 --> 00:41:15,690
At Prince Yi's residence, there was also hard evidence found. He already couldn't dispute it even if he had a hundred mouths.

379
00:41:15,690 --> 00:41:22,780
Crown Prince, it is you who Prince Yi originally wanted to poison.

380
00:41:23,350 --> 00:41:25,990
Why then do you still believe in him?

381
00:41:27,300 --> 00:41:28,900
Imperial Father,

382
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:33,420
