383
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:36,000
I still will not blame him.

384
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,790
As the elder brother, I wasn't modest.

385
00:41:38,790 --> 00:41:42,660
Even if Fifth Brother really resents me, it is normal.

386
00:41:44,770 --> 00:41:48,890
I ask that Imperial Father give a lighter sentence to Fifth Little Brother.

387
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:54,440
You truly have a broad mindset.

388
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:58,920
You are able to tolerate what others can not tolerate.

389
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:01,070
I am comforted.

390
00:42:02,620 --> 00:42:07,280
Imperial Father, you've overpraised me. It's your conduct that is my role model.

391
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:10,600
I am only following your footsteps.

392
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:14,260
Oh right.

