397
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:38,500
You have already closed the case. The deceased crown prince was killed by the Danchi people.

398
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:42,090
Li Yan is really insubordinate in saying what he did.

399
00:42:42,090 --> 00:42:45,300
But since Imperial Father has already punished him,

